    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为：从WorkerNode初始化进入Absent，扫描\"Start\"到CheckedIn。那扫描\"End\"的情况呢？是到Attended还是Error？这里LoadBalancer似乎有特殊作用？",
