        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，分两种情况：在Absent时扫描\"End\"会报错进入Error，这个错误和LoadBalancer有关；但在CheckedIn时扫描\"End\"是正常的，流转到Attended。另外CheckedIn时如果再次扫描\"Start\"，LoadBalancer会介入保持状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：Absent→CheckedIn（Start扫描），Absent→Error（End扫描+LoadBalancer），CheckedIn→Attended（End扫描）。然后CheckedIn的自循环也加上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Attended状态还需要一个自循环：扫描Start或End时，EtcdCluster会介入处理。另外Error状态要能回到Absent，通过重置或清理错误。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Attended",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Error",
        "Absent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Attended的自循环，标注EtcdCluster。Error到Absent的重置路径也画好了。不过我想确认一下，Error状态需要特别说明吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Attended",
